data.description: Don’t miss out on this beautifully updated colonial-style home nestled in the serene neighborhood of Beechwood! This home boasts four spacious bedrooms, 2 full and 1 half bathrooms , a very spacious living room, covered front porch and so much more! The large fully fenced yard is great privacy and great for entertaining on the back covered porch.  Spacious fully-floored attic above the large two car garage. New fireplace installed in family room in October 2020. Lots of space, updates, and opportunities to make this home your own! Call today to schedule your private tour!
